SUMMARY:NC Rare & Vintage Tap Event
DESCRIPTION:We’re celebrating NC Rare & Vintage coming back with some rare and vintage pours of our own! \nCome in the weekend of March 5-7 and experience 3 vintage limited-release Glass Jug beers: \n* 2022 BBA Quadratic – our delectable Belgian Quad\n* 2024 BBA Mole Deviation – Imperial Stout with several types of chili peppers\, cinnamon\, clove\, cocoa nibs & vanilla\n* 2025 Absolute Magnitude – Barrel Aged Mixed-Culture Golden Sour with Raspberry\, Blackberry\, and Strawberry
URL:https://downtowndurham.com/event/nc-rare-vintage-tap-event/2026-03-07/
