SUMMARY:LUEWWD XX: An Arm Wrestling Fundraiser
DESCRIPTION:An event not to be missed! A theatrical and competitive arm-wrestling fundraiser. Think WWE but with arm wrestling and raising money for organizations in Durham that support cisgender females\, trans and non-binary folks. There are 8 contestants with stage personas (e.g.\, Angela Slamsbury\, Tinkerhell\, Tooth Scary and so many more) and up to 4 coordinating entourage members. Contestants compete for 4 prizes: the LUEWWD arm wrestling champion\, Queen of the Losers\, Madame Moneymaker (most funds raised)\, and Durham Diva (best costume/character and entourage). Your dollars can and will influence the outcome!
URL:https://downtowndurham.com/event/luewwd-xx-an-arm-wrestling-fundraiser/
LOCATION:Motorco\, 723 Rigsbee\, Durham\, NC\, 27701\, United States
CATEGORIES:Competition,Fundraiser,Live Performance
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://downtowndurham.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/26-002-LUE-LUEWWDXX_Social_ƒ.jpg
