SUMMARY:Saturday Night DJ Dance Party
DESCRIPTION:Join the party in downtown Durham every weekend for a Saturday Night Dance Party with the best DJs in the Triangle! We alternate between our resident DJs Gay Agenda and Jorden The DJ every week. Dance the night away under a ceiling of glittering disco balls while you sip on your favorite cocktails from the area’s best bartenders. Drink specials\, no cover\, 21+ with valid ID to enter.
