SUMMARY:International Women's Day Workout
DESCRIPTION:Join Us for the International Women’s Day Workout with Beltane Strength & Fitness! \nCelebrate one year of Beltane Strength & Fitness with a strength workout class. Highlight your strength\, empowerment\, and fun with an energizing in-person session just for awesome women like you. Whether you’re a fitness newbie or a workout pro\, this event is all about moving\, sweating\, and supporting each other. \nBring your energy\, your smile\, and let’s make this day unforgettable together! Don’t miss out on celebrating International Women’s Day the active way. \nWeather permitting\, we’ll host the class outside\, so dress accordingly! \nEach ticket includes one draft beer\, wine\, cider\, or THC beverage. Get your spot here! \n 
URL:https://downtowndurham.com/event/international-womens-day-workout/
LOCATION:The Glass Jug Downtown\, 545 Foster Street\, Suite 10\, Durham\, 27701
CATEGORIES:Brewery,Fitness,Wines, Spirits, Beer and Cheer
