SUMMARY:Fused Glass Pet Portraits
DESCRIPTION:Taught by glass artist Robyn Cook.\nIn this class students will create a 5 x 7 creation of their pet using chunky frit. Students will need to bring a 5 x 7 inch photo or drawing of their pet to be used as a template.\nSkills of cutting\, grinding\, and sawing glass will be taught and perfected. Previous experience encouraged but not necessary.\nGlass pieces will be fired after class and ready for pick up approximately 1-2 weeks after class. You will be contacted to arrange pickup
URL:https://downtowndurham.com/event/fused-glass-pet-portraits-5/
LOCATION:Fusion Gallery\, 419 Foster St.\, Durham\, 27701\, United States
CATEGORIES:Art,Classes & Workshops,Craft,Date Night,Pets,Singles & Dating
