SUMMARY:Trivia Night at Ponysaurus Brewing Co.
DESCRIPTION:Show off your smarty pants at Ponysaurus Brewing Co.’s weekly Trivia Night every Monday at 6:30pm! We’ll test your knowledge of the useless information you learned watching Jeopardy\, binge-watching Netflix\, and studying for high school geography. Grab a pint\, some pizza\, and put your noggin’ to good use at our Durham pizzeria and beer garden! \nBe sure to get here early to snag a table\, set up your phones to enter answers virtually\, and get your team revved for some drinking and thinking with our hosts\, Geeks Who Drink! At the end of the night\, Ponysaurus Brewing Co. will award prizes in the shape of beer to first and second place\, as well as the team with the least amount of points and the team with the best team name!
